<h3>What is the Flexible box model?</h3>
<br>
<dt>Flexible box model</dt>
<dd>
  <p>is a new CSS box model, that determines how the boxes are distributed inside other boxes and the way they share the available space.</p>
  <p>You can read the <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-flexbox/">specification here</a>.</p>
</dd>
